# Runtime state — regenerated daily by nightly automation.
# Only the generic dream default and the directory placeholder ship with the
# repo. Feed configuration, host inventories, reports, and incidents are
# operator-specific runtime data even when they are authored rather than
# regenerated.
#
# Rule: runtime state is excluded. Curated product documentation belongs under
# a public product-doc path, not in this runtime namespace.

_state/**

# ── preserved from original ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
!_state/
!_state/dream-config.yaml
!_state/.gitkeep

# Active-task registry is operator-local runtime truth.
# Public repos should ship examples/active-tasks.sample.json instead.

# Capability inventories, MCP graduation candidates, token budgets, upgrade
# reports, and incident records stay private under the blanket rule above.

# Per-Lead mailbox state — operator-local, regenerated at runtime.
departments/*/inbox/*.md
departments/*/active/*.md
departments/*/outbox/*.md
departments/*/archive/
departments/*/archive/*.md
!departments/*/archive/
!departments/*/archive/.gitkeep
!departments/*/inbox/.gitkeep
!departments/*/active/.gitkeep
!departments/*/outbox/.gitkeep

# Per-CLI local state (Gemini, etc)
.gemini/
!model-lanes/gemini/.gemini/
!model-lanes/gemini/.gemini/agents/
!model-lanes/gemini/.gemini/agents/*.md

# Temp files from atomic writes
**/*.tmp
**/*.tmp.*

# Python / uv ephemeral envs
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# Claude Code per-project local settings (path allowlists, etc — operator-specific)
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# Private operator-fact overlays — companions to genericized public docs; never public.
# (e.g. chrono/operator-setup.local.md holds the operator's real CDP endpoint + enabled
# bounty-platform set that operator-setup.md genericizes away.)
**/*.local.md

# Obsidian local UI state
.obsidian/workspace*
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/plugins/*/data.json
.superpowers/

# Specialist/config backups (created by harness edits) — never commit
*.bak.*

# Raw model-run transcripts (large; deliverables are the .md files)
_state/audit-*/sol-*.txt
_state/audit-*/gemini-*.txt
_state/debug-*/sol-*.txt

# Operator-local runtime working-state — NOT portfolio content (mirrors mailbox/_state handling).
# Carries live session state, bounty-op intel, and personal notes; must never publish.
departments/*/current.md
departments/*/memory.md
chrono/current.md
chrono/memory.md

# Operator-local process exhaust — retained locally, excluded from public exports.
/_archive/
/projects/
/docs/handoffs/
/docs/lineage.md

# phantom KG dirs from unexpanded CHRONO_VAULT_ROOT (P0-8) — never track
**/${CHRONO_VAULT_ROOT}/

# Private memory and graph-store artifacts — defense in depth.
_state/bounty/**
**/kg.db*
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm

# Lane-local runtime config + secrets — never track (hold locally).
model-lanes/*/.gemini/settings.json
.env
.env.*
*.log
/logs/
**/*secret*.json
**/*.key
**/*.pem
